"You have been warned. You will be considered an enemy of %s if you do not "
"stop your illegal activities."
msgstr ""
"Has sido advertido. Serás considerado enemigo de%ssi no pones fin a tus "
"actividades ilegales."

#: data/scripts/entity/merchants/smugglersmarket.lua
msgid "You have no stolen goods on you."
msgstr "No lleva consigo ningún objeto robado."

#: data/scripts/entity/merchants/smugglersmarket.lua
msgid "You have to be docked to the station to unbrand goods!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tienes que estar atracado en la estación para quitar la marca de los "
"productos!"

#: data/scripts/entity/merchants/scrapyard.lua
msgid "You need a salvaging license for this sector."
msgstr "Necesitas una licencia de salvamento para este sector."

#: data/scripts/entity/merchants/scrapyard.lua
msgid "You will not get refunds for crews or turrets!"
msgstr "¡No recibirás reembolsos por tripulaciones o torretas!"

#: data/scripts/entity/merchants/smugglersmarket.lua
msgid ""
"You'll find members for nearly everything on this station, if the coin is "
"right."
msgstr ""
"Encontrarás miembros para casi todo en esta estación, si la moneda es "
"correcta."

#: data/scripts/entity/merchants/scrapyard.lua
msgid ""
"Your salvaging license has expired. You may no longer salvage in this area."
msgstr ""
"Su licencia de salvamento ha caducado. Ya no podrás realizar salvamentos en "
"esta área."

#: data/scripts/entity/merchants/scrapyard.lua
msgid ""
"Your salvaging license in %s has expired. You may no longer salvage in this "
